query:
SELECT st.id, st.ticketNumber, st.userId, st.name, st.email, st.phone, u.email as userEmail, u.name as userName
FROM supportTickets st
LEFT JOIN user u ON st.userId = u.id
WHERE st.ticketNumber = '90001';
